text:
I've kept this video with me to listen to it during this week, when I had some free time for myself, in the early mornings and late evenings. I can't express how much it warms my heart to hear you talk about this experience, and how happy it makes me that you all could meet, not just in Myth, but also with some Council members. The pandemic has probably disrupted many previous plans, but one unexpected result of it was making encountering those you hold dear even more special, and you sharing this experience with us contributed to vividly imagine and feel how wonderful this short time has been for you all. 
I hope it will be the first of many, I absolutely agree with the anniversary idea, it's a lovely initiative, and I think it will also be something nice primarily for you performers too, without always focusing on the fans, whom will be already happy with one or two off-collab videos like the arm-wrestling, but also and more importantly with knowing you all are together and treasuring your time with each other.
